A **fast, colorized, cross-platform security checker** for lab environments!  
Scan hosts with Nmap, hash detected services, and automatically block high-risk ports via firewall.  

---

## ‚ö° Features

- ‚úÖ Cross-platform: Windows & Linux compatible  
- ‚úÖ Nmap scanning with XML parsing  
- ‚úÖ SHA-256 hashing for safe storage of service info  
- ‚úÖ Automatic firewall blocking for high-risk ports  
- ‚úÖ Colorful console output using Colorama  
- ‚úÖ Configurable high-risk ports

